{
  "texts": [
    "For example, we have investigated the use of META-AGENT performing random explorations (Xiang et al., 2023; Murty et al., 2024) in virtual environments to replace the process of task and trajectory synthesis through self-instruct and zero-shot planning.",
    "We plan to conduct further research on applying AUTOACT to a wider range of tasks based on this in the future.",
    "Boosting Knowledge via Self-Instruct.",
    "As analyzed in §5, the planning performance of AU-TOACT can be limited by the model's ability to access internal knowledge through self-instruct.",
    "While the current phenomenon allows us to achieve lightweight self-differentiation in terms of parameters and data, it is still necessary to research how to enrich knowledge as much as possible within the constraints of limited data."
  ]
}